    "description": "<strong>神说：一切从加班开始！</strong><br><br>好不容易到了五一黄金周，幻想着去青青草原度假的社畜Newty却收到了来自上司的催稿。<br>他打开电脑，却发现电脑中了莫名奇妙的病毒，他熟悉的软都变得古怪起来。<br>而这时，他的桌宠Ema竟然有了自己的意识。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3045390/extras/02bc303559d05915898d9f8d4e63efb6.poster.avif?t=1746464569\" width=592 height=334 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3045390/extras/02bc303559d05915898d9f8d4e63efb6.webm?t=1746464569\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3045390/extras/02bc303559d05915898d9f8d4e63efb6.mp4?t=1746464569\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>错过ddl，就要被老板打爆狗头！</strong><br>Newty与Ema开始尝试拯救这个濒临毁灭的软件世界。<br>然而，这场通往加班的旅途才刚刚开始，更大的谜团还在前方等待他们……......<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>游戏特色：</strong></h2>支持双人游玩！支持双人游玩！支持双人游玩！<br><br>在这个像素风格的软件世界里，和你的朋友一起，扮演社畜Newty和他的桌宠Ema，合作利用电脑中尚存的功能来解谜，通过被病毒干扰的界面，逐一修复各个办公软件。<br><br>在PS（Pixelshop）——体验色块与图层的碰撞！利用画笔，橡皮等绘图工具，玩转画布，走出与众不同的道路。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3045390/extras/9d11f09a23c8d6df1a5157dbc2283e7a.poster.avif?t=1746464569\" width=592 height=334 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3045390/extras/9d11f09a23c8d6df1a5157dbc2283e7a.webm?t=1746464569\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3045390/extras/9d11f09a23c8d6df1a5157dbc2283e7a.mp4?t=1746464569\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3045390/extras/c1557d45ac50945c13b7c248d0aa73b9.poster.avif?t=1746464569\" width=592 height=334 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3045390/extras/c1557d45ac50945c13b7c248d0aa73b9.webm?t=1746464569\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3045390/extras/c1557d45ac50945c13b7c248d0aa73b9.mp4?t=1746464569\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>在PR（PixelRecorder）——面对时间与轨迹的错乱，录制角色运动轨迹，解锁通往门的途径。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3045390/extras/18787818b906578756d66f583f82a13b.poster.avif?t=1746464569\" width=592 height=334 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3045390/extras/18787818b906578756d66f583f82a13b.webm?t=1746464569\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3045390/extras/18787818b906578756d66f583f82a13b.mp4?t=1746464569\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3045390/extras/d6a1c5254e01731d97cb763438e9fa1c.poster.avif?t=1746464569\" width=592 height=334 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3045390/extras/d6a1c5254e01731d97cb763438e9fa1c.webm?t=1746464569\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3045390/extras/d6a1c5254e01731d97cb763438e9fa1c.mp4?t=1746464569\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>再也不用担心老板神出鬼没了，因为你的Boss来啦！<br>每一章末尾均设有特殊boss。利用本章习得的技能击（胖）败（揍）他们。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3045390/extras/86001dc82df6eace409b44970be105c1.poster.avif?t=1746464569\"